question: Sophie has five times as many TikTok friends as Sophia. Jessica has one times as many friends on TikTok as Sophia. If Sophie has 93 friends on TikTok, how many TikTok friends does Jessica have?
answer:
Sophia has 93/5 = <<93/5=18>>18 TikTok friends.
Jessica has 1*18 = <<1*18=18>>18 TikTok friends.
#### 18
